Package: SimilaR
Version: 1.0.8
Date: 2020-06-26
Title: R Source Code Similarity Evaluation
Description: An implementation of a novel method to quantify the
        similarity of the code-base of R functions by means of program
        dependence graphs. Possible use cases include detection of code
        clones for improving software quality and of plagiarism amongst
        students' assignments.
URL: https://github.com/bartoszukm/SimilaR
BugReports: https://github.com/bartoszukm/SimilaR/issues
